title: North Carolina Republican Party
deleted: The most recent version of the North Carolina Republican platform was released on June 7, 2013. It contains ten articles and was formed by 13 district representatives and 3 Republican chair members.<ref name="ncgop.org">http://www.ncgop.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/2013-Platform-Passed.pdf</ref>

The party supports free enterprise economics with little government regulation and taxation.<ref>[http://03481cf.netsolhost.com/WordPress/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/2011-NCGOP-Platform-As-Adopted.pdf]</ref>
English should be the official language of the United States.<ref name="ncgop.org"/>
